did.origination: Retail, Wholesale and Department Store Union (RWDSU); RWDSU Local 1199 Drug and Hospital Union
did.repository: Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: This collection includes meeting minutes, financial records, membership records, collective bargaining files, for the Hospital Division of Local 1199.
